        <text>&lt;p&gt;Hi {!$Record.Site__r.Office_Admin__r.FirstName},&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You have a new starter, {!$Record.First_Name__c} {!$Record.Last_Name__c} - {!$Record.Department__c} starting on {!$Record.Start_Date__c} at {!$Record.Site__r.Name}.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please complete the following list of tasks:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Order welcome gift, equipment &amp;amp; resources - &lt;strong&gt;due on {!FourWeeksBefore}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Build caseload in accordance with discipline specific ramp up schedule. First initial to be booked on Day 3 with Supervisor - &lt;strong&gt;due on {!ThreeWeeksBefore}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add to capacity tracker - &lt;strong&gt;due on {!TwoWeeksBefore}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Schedule welcome breakfast (Tuesday Week 2 of cycle)&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt; - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;due on {!TwoWeeksBefore}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add to team meeting in Lumary session&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt; - &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;due on {!TwoWeeksBefore}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set up new starter desk - &lt;strong&gt;due on {!OneWeekBefore}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Site induction (WHS walk through). &lt;em&gt;Note: If and office Manager is not at a specific site, the OM is to coordinate site induction through the site Team Leader or an AHA&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;- due on {!$Record.Start_Date__c}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Complete Headshots and provide codes&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;- due on {!$Record.Start_Date__c}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Accept PRODA request (admin team lead only)&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;- due on {!$Record.Start_Date__c}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Note: If Team Leader is not at a specific site, the onsite induction will sit with the Office Manager of that site&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;- due on {!$Record.Start_Date__c}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Regards,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Better Rehab&lt;/p&gt;</text>
